Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.64,1:00:12.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}(هيجيري)-سان؟
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.75,1:00:13.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\be1}لمَ؟
